  [ ] Create requisition_approvals table (schema above)
  [ ] On POST .../submit: create 3 approval rows (stage 1 pending, 2+3 waiting)
  [ ] On re-submission (revision → submit): reset approval chain
  [ ] PATCH .../approval: implement all 4 actions with stage transition rules
  [ ] Enforce permission-based stage ownership (403 if wrong role)
